"  Dressing:","3 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","2 tablespoons olive oil","1 tablespoon country-style Dijon mustard","1 teaspoon minced fresh or 1/4 teaspoon dried thyme","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon celery seeds","  Salad:","1 3/4 pounds fingerling potatoes","1 cup sugar snap peas, trimmed","1 cup broccoli florets","1/4 cup diced red bell pepper","1/4 cup diced green bell pepper","1/4 cup diced yellow bell pepper","1/4 cup chopped green onions"